            <noteGrp type="workDesc">
               <note type="description">Extract from an exegesis on the Fātiḥa, why it is called the opening, etc. The original source is not known, but our researches show that it is a precious copy of a text also found on 1a of Evkaf Muzesi 1933, the copy of Fuṣūṣ al-ḥikam in SQ’s handwriting, which is now not fully readable.</note>
               <note type="structure">Structure of Work</note>
